Eliza Schneider https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eliza_Schneider 0 Eliza Jane Schneider is an American actress, singer-songwriter, playwright, dialect coach and dialectologist, and voice artist. She has appeared on television and as a voiceover actress on video games and cartoons. She also performs various musical and stage shows.
